The project will use a secondary dataset from Kaggle titled:

**Retail Sales Data with Seasonal Trends and Marketing**

The dataset will be treated as a sample of retail sales records that can be used to study relationships between discounts, revenue, product category, marketing spend, and seasonal trends.

