## Data Wrangling Plan

The raw records will be prepared for analysis by:

1. Importing the CSV file into R
2. Cleaning column names
3. Checking missing values and duplicates
4. Converting date variables into date format
5. Creating month, quarter, and season variables
6. Creating discount groups
7. Summarizing sales outcomes by category, location, and time period

