## RO5: Discounts, Holidays, and Seasonality

**Research Objective:** Examine whether discounts perform differently during holidays or seasonal periods.

| Element | Plan |
|---|---|
| Independent Variables | Discount percentage, holiday effect, month, day of week |
| Dependent Variable | Units sold or sales revenue |
| Seasonal Variables | Month, quarter, holiday effect, day of week |
