---

## RO5: Wrangling and Visualization Plan

**Plan for data wrangling:**

- Extract month and quarter from date
- Compare holiday and non-holiday records
- Summarize monthly sales by discount group

**Plan for data visualization:**

- Monthly sales line chart
- Holiday vs non-holiday bar chart
- Day-of-week sales heatmap

```{r}
#| label: ro5-visual-template
#| eval: false

retail_tidy |> 
  group_by(month, discount_group) |> 
  summarise(total_revenue = sum(sales_revenue_usd, na.rm = TRUE), .groups = "drop") |> 
  ggplot(aes(x = month, y = total_revenue, group = discount_group)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  labs(
    title = "Monthly Sales Revenue by Discount Group",
    x = "Month",
    y = "Total Sales Revenue"
  )
```

