## Limitations

This project evaluates sales volume and sales revenue, but it may not directly measure profit.

Possible limitations include:

- The dataset may not include cost of goods sold
- Discount effects may differ by unobserved customer behavior
- The dataset is secondary and may not represent every retail environment
- Sales revenue does not always equal profitability

